{"tid":2017157,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"主任可裁定選票有效性","createTime":"2020-05-15T02:39:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T03:26:00.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b161f544ac6c8064b7c46c9290aa8f9f49a14662","tid":2017157,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:39:56.000Z","msg":"全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200515/CAJC7ETSXGL6DAZ5CSRNYFETQQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FCAJC7ETSXGL6DAZ5CSRNYFETQQ%2F&d=Q2wtXUBBwx94fvyzOWO%2FRU%2BK1qRryb6uhbKsh0ikEBY%3D&h=4f8d2f24\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200515%2FCAJC7ETSXGL6DAZ5CSRNYFETQQ%2F&h=ee927999\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200515/CAJC7ETSXGL6DAZ5CSRNYFETQQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n主任可裁定選票有效性<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200515/large/1589474122_8933.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200515%2Flarge%2F1589474122_8933.jpg&h=315f7f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n票站職員基本上全由選舉事務處聘公務員兼職。資料圖片&lt;br /&gt;<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】票站職員有五個職級，最高級、權力最大的是票站主任，酬金亦是最高，約為2.4萬元，但並非每個公務員都可以申請做票站主任，要薪酬點達39點的人員才可以申請。翻查。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n助理負責核對選民身份<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：建制區選大敗賴票站職員<br />\n<br />\n票站職員基本上全由選舉事務處聘公務員兼職，最低級是投票助理，只要符合薪金點10的水平即可申。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n投票合法進行，以及維持投票站運作。如果有人在「禁止拉票區」拉票 ，票站主任有責任維持這些區。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n重要權力，就是裁定問題選票是否有效 。<br />\n<br />\n但投票助理也有一定權力及重要性，因他們負責核。。。。。。。。<br />\n劃走已投票選民，這個工序亦是坊間最常質疑種票。。。。。。。。。。。。。「被投票」，登記冊上名字已被劃走。<br />\n<br />\n■記者歐陽聯發"},{"pid":"f747e7e6ccfa6b48af1b15ffc7962fc8511eecac","tid":2017157,"uid":28432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T02:48:24.000Z","msg":"D新聞全部。。。做乜 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p